es/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但好想知有咩其他可以幫到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebe2ec2e5ee9d76893517a1b8d166b543e65325b","tid":85864,"uid":59748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T15:55:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都試過1個月2次。而家一個月一次，但M前一定又肚痛又爆瘡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我又唔係次次既 但通常第一日都會好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3deb5c175dc17172b1ce0bc91c796560032a1f22","tid":85864,"uid":59748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T15:56:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇下醫生好，我都唔準但只會遲唔會早<br />\n之前睇過醫生，食左d調理身體嘅藥，依加叫準左少少，唔會遲五六日咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都試過有排每個月遲2個星期先黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都食緊中藥，唔知有冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但好想知有咩其他可以幫到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絲打 中醫點講"},{"pid":"4ea4d5bfa31510bd09408a9ebacca1d8528982d7","tid":85864,"uid":76652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T15:59:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇下醫生好，我都唔準但只會遲唔會早<br />\n之前睇過醫生，食左d調理身體嘅藥，依加叫準左少少，唔會遲五六日咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n醫生點講？我亂到癡線，月頭中尾都會來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嘩，你都好亂下。但係咪每日幾滴甘黎成個月？<br />\n我有朋友都係黎成個月，then佢去左西醫度開止血藥俾佢食，而家再睇中醫"},{"pid":"e8a8622ef599d973e4b6fb32b23792a6fada7c9f","tid":85864,"uid":8650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T16:03:50.000Z","msg":"我都係廿歲，都係勁亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"931f01d8dc580a0e5be8eda64f7ad849940c130f","tid":85864,"uid":53648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T16:04:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bfd53b8bc2464d4510e24d5dd29f884970347a8b","tid":85864,"uid":47244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T16:05:03.000Z","msg":"睇過中醫 中醫會話盡量唔好食生冷嘢<br />\n之後睇過西醫 西醫會幫你check超聲波睇下個子宮 西醫話如果月經黎得太頻密 例如一個月多過一次而經常都係咁既話 可能生瘤 另外如果經期唔係一個月一次例如季經 可能多囊性卵巢<br />\n如果有以上症狀最好去睇下專科照下超聲波"},{"pid":"7f19b8595c1396f64089cd444aac4eed63dc448c","tid":85864,"uid":76652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T16:06:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇下醫生好，我都唔準但只會遲唔會早<br />\n之前睇過醫生，食左d調理身體嘅藥，依加叫準左少少，唔會遲五六日咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都試過有排每個月遲2個星期先黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都食緊中藥，唔知有冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但好想知有咩其他可以幫到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絲打 中醫點講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢話陰虛，即係西醫嘅荷爾蒙失調。<br />\n但我知肝鬱(即係壓力大心情差)，都會月經失調。<br />\n建議絲打都係去睇中醫，交囇俾佢處理算數。<br />\n我月經唔正常左好多年，搞唔點唯有揾中醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我唔到最後都唔敢揾西醫食避孕藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6129679b628eb4e498d0c7357c8c11746ee1883b","tid":85864,"uid":76652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T16:09:16.000Z","msg":"Btw 我以後好鐘意飲凍野食凍野，黎M果時就好多血塊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家戒左凍野半年，d血塊冇囇，好神奇"},{"pid":"42a1787e8487b1b9d0434f6e381c5fe1fe11edd2","tid":85864,"uid":28873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T16:23:0