eck 發現有朱古力瘤 不過你check過咁就無問題啦"},{"pid":"504b1eb6eab91001420cba62bac7bc4e02c5613f","tid":85864,"uid":59748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T16:57:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇過中醫 中醫會話盡量唔好食生冷嘢<br />\n之後睇過西醫 西醫會幫你check超聲波睇下個子宮 西醫話如果月經黎得太頻密 例如一個月多過一次而經常都係咁既話 可能生瘤 另外如果經期唔係一個月一次例如季經 可能多囊性卵巢<br />\n如果有以上症狀最好去睇下專科照下超聲波</blockquote><br />\n我咁多年來第二次咋 唔會係瘤掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59e1c297836c0eaf41ac89197c7f0cbb92567297","tid":85864,"uid":47244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T16:57:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Btw 我以後好鐘意飲凍野食凍野，黎M果時就好多血塊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家戒左凍野半年，d血塊冇囇，好神奇</blockquote><br />\n啲中醫係建議盡量唔好飲凍嘢"},{"pid":"0788f60858fc07df40ea013de272cc8d657e43a3","tid":85864,"uid":59748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T16:58:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌 成廿歲人<br />\nM期仲係唔準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要一個月來兩次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咩問題？ 好多女人都唔準架啦，點解一定要迫佢準？</blockquote><br />\n我亂得好誇張 月頭中尾亂咁來"},{"pid":"2130ac01edff554d435d9ee6833513a0bf6933b0","tid":85864,"uid":15954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T16:59:36.000Z","msg":"食避孕藥"},{"pid":"c2c3100c62c73b7e4564e5cce0afa683ddec3fb0","tid":85864,"uid":56891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T17:00:31.000Z","msg":"去檢查，如果子宮無事<br />\n就去睇中醫調理"},{"pid":"a45ebf6f448ba2f40bae0c1aaf49df149df6e1f8","tid":85864,"uid":47244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T17:00:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇過中醫 中醫會話盡量唔好食生冷嘢<br />\n之後睇過西醫 西醫會幫你check超聲波睇下個子